metadata.name: FeaturedTags GET /api/v1/featured_tags when the requesting user has featured tags returns only the featured tags belonging to the requesting user

sql_query.sql: SELECT 1 AS one FROM "oauth_access_tokens" WHERE "oauth_access_tokens"."token" = $1 LIMIT $2
SELECT 1 AS one FROM "oauth_access_tokens" WHERE "oauth_access_tokens"."token" = $1 AND "oauth_access_tokens"."id" != $2 LIMIT $3
SELECT "featured_tags".* FROM "featured_tags" WHERE "featured_tags"."account_id" = $1 ORDER BY "featured_tags"."statuses_count" DESC
